Scattershot/Nemesis Enforcer:



Nemesis Enforcer saluted. "YES, SIR!" he screamed into his comm., running for 
the conference room.  He collided with Scattershot, both of them falling down.

Enforcer got up slowly, kicking Scattershot.  "Idiot!  Watch where you're 
going."

Nemesis ran for the conference room, stopping and letting himself calm down.  
Stepping into the conference room, he saluted Zardus.

"Reporting for duty, sir."

---

Scattershot got up, flipping Nemesis off, though Enforcer's back was turned 
to him.  "Your mutha!," he said, a mood swing happening, "I like that astro 
punk!  He's got spunk and moxy, reminds me of me when I was younger.  That 
dumbskidplate punk!  I'll beat the living slag out of him next time I see 
him!" the VERY psychotic Predacon headed for the CR chambers.
